==Notes==
*Located south of [[Ice Dungeon]], north of the Shrine of Compassion, and northwest of [[Minoc]].
*Receives the 50% Dungeon Skill Gain Bonus.

==Champion Spawn==
Beware adventurers, within this treacherous dungeon [[Dungeon_Bosses#Arch_Demon|the Arch Demon]] can be found! [[Dungeon_Bosses#Arch_Demon|The Arch Demon]] is one of the many [[Dungeon_Bosses|Dungeon Bosses]] that inhabit the lands of Sosaria. 

==Dungeon Boss==
Be careful, as you may first encounter [[Champion_Spawns#Lord_Oaks_-_Skull_of_Enlightenment|Lord Oaks]] at the entrance of Wrong. [[Champion_Spawns#Lord_Oaks_-_Skull_of_Enlightenment|Lord Oaks|Lord Oaks]] is one of the many [[Champion_Spawns|Champions]] that can be found in Sosaria.
